qas.question: What year did the Dutch abandon the island?
Which colony did the Dutch abandon the island for?

context: <a0_0>The Dutch Republic<a0_0/> formally made claim to Saint Helena in 1633, although there is no evidence that they ever occupied, colonised or fortified it. By <a1_0>1651<a1_0/>, the Dutch had mainly abandoned the island in favour of their colony at the <a2_0>Cape of Good Hope.
